'Lackland's got a back room. The word's //Valletta//.'

Copper's gurning, more in speed than anger.

St. John leads you out: 'Next time, knock on the right door.'

(set: $confidence to $confidence - 8)

(if: $knowsCopperSecret is false)[(set: $knowsCopperSecret to true)

