<svg id="dean-lamp-svg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="145" height="720" style="float:right;margin:0 -0.5em 1em 0.8em;overflow:hidden;"><defs><radialGradient id="dslamp" cx="72%" cy="11%" r="62%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#d4a060" stop-opacity="0.55"/><stop offset="25%" stop-color="#c89060" stop-opacity="0.25"/><stop offset="60%" stop-color="#c89060" stop-opacity="0.08"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#c89060" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient></defs><g transform="scale(0.853)"><rect x="-50" y="-60" width="280" height="380" fill="url(#dslamp)"/><g fill="none" stroke="#c8a86a" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="108" cy="38" r="6" stroke-width="1.6"/><line x1="108" y1="44" x2="108" y2="52" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="85" y1="85" x2="108" y2="52" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="108" y1="52" x2="131" y2="85" stroke-width="2"/><line x1="82" y1="85" x2="134" y2="85" stroke-width="2.2"/><path d="M86,85 C83,93 82,107 83,121 C84,133 89,143 108,146 C127,143 132,133 133,121 C134,107 133,93 130,85" stroke-width="1.8"/><line x1="108" y1="85" x2="108" y2="146" stroke-width="1.1"/><path d="M86,114 C93,111 102,113 108,114 C114,113 123,111 130,114" stroke-width="1.1"/><line x1="118" y1="88" x2="129" y2="110" stroke-width="0.85" stroke-opacity="0.55"/><path d="M103,146 C101,154 103,164 108,167 C113,164 115,154 113,146" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M95,262 C96,248 124,236 126,208 C128,180 118,163 108,148" stroke-width="2.4"/><circle cx="95" cy="262" r="9" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M86,254 C79,246 78,235 85,233 C91,232 93,244 95,256" stroke-width="1.3"/><path d="M104,254 C111,246 112,235 105,233 C99,232 97,244 95,256" stroke-width="1.3"/><line x1="95" y1="271" x2="95" y2="9999" stroke-width="3.2"/><path d="M86,396 C82,386 83,376 89,374 C93,373 95,380 95,390" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M104,396 C108,386 107,376 101,374 C97,373 95,380 95,390" stroke-width="1.4"/><ellipse cx="95" cy="399" rx="14" ry="5" stroke-width="1.6"/><path d="M86,548 C82,538 83,528 89,526 C93,525 95,532 95,542" stroke-width="1.4"/><path d="M104,548 C108,538 107,528 101,526 C97,525 95,532 95,542" stroke-width="1.4"/><ellipse cx="95" cy="551" rx="14" ry="5" stroke-width="1.6"/></g></g></svg>

<h1 class="game-title" style="font-size:1.7em;">DREAM STREET SHUFFLE</h1>\
{(unless: $alba is an array)[(set: $alba to (a:))]
(unless: $haunts is an array)[(set: $haunts to (a:))]
(set: $returns to $returns + 1)
(if: $confidence > 100)[(set: $confidence to 100)]
(if: $confidence < 0)[(set: $confidence to 0)]
(if: $sobriety > 100)[(set: $sobriety to 100)]
(if: $sobriety < 0)[(set: $sobriety to 0)]
(if: $sobriety <= 0)[(goto: "Coach and Horses lock")]
(if: $confidence <= 5 and not (($alba contains $alba1) and ($alba contains $alba2) and ($alba contains $alba3)))[[[Give up on the book|No more]]]
(else-if: $confidence <= 25)[<span class="greyed-out">//You're losing your nerve. What would cheer you up?//</span>]
(if: $wasBeaten is true and $visitedInterval is true)[<span class="fetch-glimpse">You see him then: yourself, walking ahead of you down Greek Street toward Centre Point. He does not look back. He walks the way a man walks when he has made a decision. You know where he is going. You have always known.</span>]
}
<span class="scene-date">23.11.73</span>

<span class="scene-location">Dean Street, Soho, London.</span>

A heavy afternoon lingers in rainfall on the pavements though the sky has cleared now and the newborn night is cut with moonshine.

There is an atmosphere of the silver screen: as if Brando might emerge in a tight and sodden T-shirt, from any door or alleyway, anytime.

In your bag, you have your novel in manuscript. You need to sell it, pronto.

(if: $haunts's length >= 5)[Something shifts again. Eyes meet you and doors open like they used to. Keep on.](else-if: $haunts's length >= 3)[Something shifts. The faces start to know your face again. A girl at the French waves through the reeded glass. It's beginning to let you in.]

(if: $hadPhoneCall is true)[Aoife's voice echoes: //Try harder.// The baby. The cold flat. No milk. No heat. No time.]

(if: $metRed is true)[Where do you go?

(if: $visited's French is not true or $exploredSinceFrench is true)[[[To The French|The French]]](else:)[<span class="greyed-out">To The French (you were just there — try somewhere new)</span>]
(if: $visited's French is true)[[[To The Pillars of Hercules|Maritime interlude]]]
(if: $visited's French is true)[[[Try the Colony Room|The Colony Room Door]]]
(if: $knowsRonnies is true and $completedSetlist is false)[[[Hear the jazz at Ronnie Scott's|Ronnie Scott's]]
](else-if: $knowsRonnies is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Ronnie Scott's (you've heard the set)</span>
]\
(if: $knowsLackland is true and $knowsCopperSecret is true)[[[Go to Lackland's Office|Martin Lackland's Office]]
](else-if: $knowsLackland is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Lackland's Office (need the password)</span>
]\
(if: $knowsCecilCourt is true and $returnedPage is false)[[[Visit the antiquarian in Cecil Court|Cecil Court]]
](else-if: $returnedPage is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Cecil Court (you've returned the page)</span>
]\
(if: $hasTrishaMatchbook is true and not ($haunts contains $haunt8))[[[Try Trisha's|Failure: Trisha's]]
](else-if: $haunts contains $haunt8)[<span class="greyed-out">Trisha's (nothing more to find)</span>
]\
(if: ($alba contains $alba1) and ($alba contains $alba2) and not ($alba contains $alba3))[[[The voice|Late Lily]]
]]
(else:)[Who's that on the corner?

[[See who's there|At the Corner of Dean Street and Greek Street]]]

(if: $confidence < 40 and $hadBreather is false)[You're feeling worn down. There's a quiet doorway nearby.

[[Step into the doorway|A Doorway on Dean Street]]
](else-if: $hadBreather is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Step into the doorway</span>
]\
(if: $confidence < 50 and $sobriety < 50 and $hadChippy is false)[You're in a bad way. But there's a place you know, down a side street. The Chinese Fish and Chips.

[[Get something to eat|Chinese Fish and Chips]]
](else-if: $hadChippy is true)[<span class="greyed-out">Get something to eat</span>
]\
(if: $alba contains $alba1)[\
