As he turns from his ginger light, you catch something else on the darkness. He's still speaking.

<div class="quest-box">
<div class="quest-header">⟡ ALBA ⟡</div>
<div class="quest-description">
Soho lets you lose things: your books, your money, years. Those who survive here learn to take things back.

There are three lines of an aubade out in the darkness. Find them before dawn and you'll get out alive.

Miss them and you'll be another Dean Street dream.
</div>
<div class="quest-objective">FIND THE THREE LINES BEFORE DAWN</div>
</div>

[[Dream on|The First Line]]


:: LINE 2 {"position":"900,200","size":"100,100"}
Just off the beach is a bar called The Green Sea. It's mostly old men playing cribbage, and on its wall is a portrait of Ban Ali, though standards have slipped or morals have grown less important; there are women here now, white women, at least.

At the back round the second biggest table is a family you know, playing cards with an Italian deck.

Among them, with his back to you, is your old friend. The eldest of the kids. You see him before he sees you.

(link: "Listen")[(set: $alba to $alba + (a: $alba2))
(set: $albaGiven's street2 to true)

He speaks. The family roars on around, as his old sister winds a trick, him but you hear only this:

<div class="revelation-box">
<em>"$alba2"</em>
</div>

<strong>THE SECOND LINE OF THREE</strong>

[[Return to Dean Street|Dean Street]]]


:: LINE 3 {"position":"1100,200","size":"100,100"}
If dawn was something you could hear, you would hear it now. Your ears are attuned in a way that your eyes can never be. But you trust your eyes more, so the thrum of dawn approaching, registers as a silent alarm.

Then you see it, the sky tearing patches from itself and bleeding red, orange, green through the night's bandage.

(link: "Closer")[(set: $alba to $alba + (a: $alba3))
(set: $albaGiven's street3 to true)

The last line comes out of your own throat, as you cry, 'I wish that I was never…' then:

<div class="revelation-box">
<em>"$alba3"</em>
</div>

It is written. You shall get out alive.

<strong>THE THIRD LINE — THE ALBA IS COMPLETE</strong>

[[Soho!|Things turn up]]]


