:: PP Victory {"position":"1200,2550","size":"100,100"}
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 20)

<div class="pp-arena">
<div class="pp-score"><span class="pp-result-win">★ VICTORY ★</span></div>
</div>

(if: $opponent is "Harsent")[Harsent laughs. Hands you a folded paper.

'A line. Can't find its poem. Maybe you can.']
(else:)[Clegg hands you a slip of paper.

'From an old pamphlet. Seventeenth century. Take it.']

You unfold the paper:

<div class="revelation-box">
<em>"Between the acting of a dreadful thing / And the first motion, all the interim is / Like a phantasma, or a hideous dream."</em>
</div>

It's not the Alba. But it's something.

(if: not ($haunts contains $haunt5))[(if: $hauntExplained is false)[(set: $hauntExplained to true)
<div class="lore-box">
<strong>⟡ HAUNTS ⟡</strong>

Tonight, Soho will mark you. Here, in our mutual dream, we call them 'haunts'. You'll gather them as you wander the night and its stages. Seek them: you'll need them to get out.
</div>]
(set: $haunts to $haunts + (a: $haunt5))

