<div class="haunt-name">THE DELIVERY</div>
<div class="haunt-description">Shelley Never Dies.</div>
</div>]

[[Back to Dean Street|Dean Street]]


:: Ride Jeffrey Bernard's cow {"position":"900,1200","size":"100,100"}
You cry, 'Soho! Soho!' and mount the beast.

Every cabbie knows the streets run east to west. You just need the right order.

[[Ride!|Cow wrong 1]]


:: Cow wrong 1 {"position":"1000,1200","size":"100,100"}
Down Dean, up Wardour, through Poland, past Berwick, along Greek, onto Frith.

The cow stops dead. Snorts. Wrong way.

[[Try again|Cow wrong 2]]


:: Cow wrong 2 {"position":"1100,1200","size":"100,100"}
Along Wardour, down Berwick, up Poland, through Dean, past Frith, onto Greek.

She bucks. Still wrong.

[[One more time|Cow ride success]]


:: Cow ride success {"position":"1200,1200","size":"100,100"}
Down Greek, up Frith, along Dean, through Wardour, past Berwick, onto Poland.

//Go For Dinner With Billy Piper.//

The cow knows. She runs.

(set: $confidence to $confidence + 20)
(set: $sobriety to $sobriety + 10)

(if: $haunts's length >= 7)[It's coming up!

[[Face the dawn|LINE 3]]]
(else:)[[[Return to the street|Dean Street]]]


