::Success: Trisha&#39;s {"position":"2100,1450"}
As you walk in you see a woman who was a friend of yours years ago, who somehow keeps some part in your affections. Her voice reminds you somebody else you used to see in Soho, who was a friend of John St. John's, when you were all much younger than this. Soho is hers now; she knows all the bouncers. In you go.

[[Trisha's|Trisha's]]

::The Painter&#39;s Gaze {"position":"500,900"}
He looks at you like, painterly, he looked when you were his subject.

